{"head":{"cizm_thread_id":"S1fpYk2Rx","cizm_path":"https://www.collaborizm.com/thread/S1fpYk2Rx","category":"general","date":"2017-04-24T21:10:17.692Z","description":"I wanted @Robert and @Anton to distinguish inline code from regular text and I gave them the CSS too. \n\nWhile the CSS gave me what Iâ€¦","title":"Adding bugs to collaborizm.","stripped_title":"adding-bugs-to-collaborizm","route":"blog/adding-bugs-to-collaborizm.md","layout":"Post"},"body":"<p>I wanted <span class='md-at-person'><a target=_blank href=\"https://www.collaborizm.com/profile/21339\">Robert</a></span> and <span class='md-at-person'><a target=_blank href=\"https://www.collaborizm.com/profile/4kvzVlj5e\">Anton</a></span> to distinguish <strong>inline code</strong> from regular text and I gave them the CSS too.</p>\n<p>While the CSS gave me what I wanted, it started overriding the syntax highlighting in <strong>block code</strong>.</p>\n<p><div>\n    <img class=\"md-img\" src='https://res.cloudinary.com/collabizm/image/upload//v1/from_markdown/pkoibmn2ff1hrffgzsvt' />\n  </div></p>\n<h2>Faulty CSS</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-clike\"><code class=\"language-clike\">code <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    background<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>color<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #f7f7f9<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    border<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid #e1e1e8<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    border<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>radius<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    color<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #dd1144<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    padding<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px 4px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    overflow<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>wrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">break</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>word<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Fix</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-clike\"><code class=\"language-clike\"><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">not</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pre<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> code <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    background<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>color<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #f7f7f9<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    border<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid #e1e1e8<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    border<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>radius<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    color<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #dd1144<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    padding<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px 4px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    overflow<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>wrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">break</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>word<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>PS: Are there prizes for fails? ðŸ˜›</p>\n<p><span class='md-hashtag-adhoc'>#Fail</span> <span class='md-hashtag-adhoc'>#fails</span></p>\n","__filename":"blog/collaborizm_posts/adding-bugs-to-collaborizm__25-04-2017.md","__url":"/blog/adding-bugs-to-collaborizm/","__resourceUrl":"/blog/adding-bugs-to-collaborizm/index.html","__dataUrl":"/blog/adding-bugs-to-collaborizm/index.html.e1c87847688488faaf83dca972db60f5.json"}